{
  "text": "The regularization parameter ρ in Equation (6) is driven by the parameters λ and s 0 [CITATION_1] , so the iteration process of λ and s 0 is equivalent to iteratively updating the regularization parameter ρ which can make the reconstruction of sound field more accurate. This is an important reason to introduce a third layer of the hierarchical prior to overcome the drawback of using a fixed regularization parameter in conventional ESM.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "206797074"
